%% FR-01 / FR-02: tranche deposit via modifyLiquidity
flowchart LR
    LP[Liquidity Provider] --> PM[PoolManager.modifyLiquidity +L]
    PM --> HK[afterAddLiquidity]
    HK --> DEC{TrancheType?}
    DEC -->|JUNIOR| J1[juniorTVL += principalValue]
    DEC -->|SENIOR| S1[enforceOnSeniorIntake]
    S1 --> S2[seniorTVL += principalValue]
    S2 --> SYNC[_syncSeniorObligation]
    J1 --> POS[TranchePosition stored]
    SYNC --> POS
    POS --> MINT[Mint jtLP or stLP]
    MINT --> CHK[feePerShareCheckpointX128 = pool cumulative]
